event.description: 192.168. 1. 1 is an IP address that belongs to C class of IP address. This IP address is very effective in making any kind of change to your existing router and effectively taking care of the problem that might arise in the future. This IP address has been accepted by ADSL router manufacturers from all over the world as a default IP address for making changes to IP address. This can be a very effective way to change password or SSID name of your router.
